cff-version: 1.2.0
message: If you use this software, please cite it as below.
title: assaio
abstract: >-
  Open-source, offline-first CLI for measuring how an organization uses AI
  coding tools: token and cost accounting, and AI-output-versus-cost
  effectiveness per project, across Claude Code, Codex CLI, Gemini CLI, and
  Cline. Survival, bug-impact, and quality correlation are future server-stage
  roadmap, not current scope.
authors:
  - name: The assaio Authors
license: Apache-2.0
version: 0.1.1
repository-code: https://github.com/assaio/assaio
url: https://github.com/assaio/assaio
date-released: 2026-07-20
